	Put something you regularly use - a mobile phone or stapler - a few feet from your desk, so you have to get up to use it. While you're standing, do a few lunges to strengthen your thighs and bum.&lt;/p&gt;" href="http://www.blogcdn.com/lifestyle.aol.co.uk/media/2011/07/woman-desk-tools-getty.jpg" data-photo-src="http://www.blogcdn.com/lifestyle.aol.co.uk/media/2011/07/woman-desk-tools-getty.jpg" data-credit="Getty">Get up</a><div class="aol-photo-caption">&lt;p&gt;
